 
<p>
  The UK plans to <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2022/jul/03/uk-home-office-plans-second-flight-to-deport-asylum-seekers-to-rwanda">try again to send refugees to Rwanda</a>, and do so before
  the start of a planned court hearing about whether it is lawful to do this.
<p>
  That would go beyond disregarding asylum seekers' human rights: it
  would show contempt for the idea that they (or any people) have
  rights.

 